ygData.msgSnippet: Now I m 33, and at 32 I hit for 53 max... still have yet to see more then that with this dam BBC that I have to get rid of... hehe As for warrior... well at 33
ygData.messageBody:
Now I'm 33, and at 32 I hit for 53 max... still have yet to see more
then that with this dam BBC that I have to get rid of... hehe

As for warrior... well at 33 I have 930 or so hps... not sure exactly,
hehe... and well warriors are good with a group, but if you cant find a
group you might as well log off :( or camp something super easy.
At this level, warriors are more equipment dependant then any other
class, maybe tied with Rogues. So to be a good warrior, you have to have
the best stuff you can get at your level, otherwise your usefulness to a
group is limited.


Eogun
